  <section line_height="10.91" font="KCQPMK+CMR10" letter_ratio="0.08"
year_ratio="0.0" cap_ratio="0.08" name_ratio="0.2465753424657534"
word_count="146" lateness="0.75" reference_score="20.35">
    <line x_offset="0.0" y_offset="135.48" spacing="0.0">Figure 3: The
classical average potential energy &lt; V &gt; for the &#x3B3; = 0.9</line>
    <line x_offset="0.0" y_offset="121.92" spacing="2.65">potential as a
function of &#x3B2;. The thin solid curves are initialized at the</line>
    <line x_offset="0.0" y_offset="108.36" spacing="2.65">metastable
&#x3B1;-minimum x = 0.9613 with the standard Monte Carlo algo-</line>
    <line x_offset="120.96" y_offset="107.42" spacing="-7.02">0</line>
    <line x_offset="140.28" y_offset="100.61"
spacing="-11.85">&#x2212;</line>
    <line x_offset="0.0" y_offset="94.8" spacing="-5.09">rithm with the
parameter q = 1 and the generalized Monte Carlo algorithm</line>
    <line x_offset="0.0" y_offset="81.24" spacing="2.65">with q = 1.5, q =
2.0 and q = 2.5. The exact result is represented by the</line>
    <line x_offset="0.0" y_offset="67.8" spacing="2.53">thick solid curve.
The results initialized at the global minimum x = 1</line>
    <line x_offset="329.4" y_offset="66.85" spacing="-7.02">0</line>
    <line x_offset="0.0" y_offset="54.24" spacing="1.71">and calculated
from the Metropolis algorithm with q = 1 and that from the</line>
    <line x_offset="0.0" y_offset="40.68" spacing="2.65">generalized Monte
Carlo algorithm with q = 1.5 are shown by the dotted</line>
    <line x_offset="0.0" y_offset="27.12" spacing="2.65">curve. All results
are obtained from 100 independently initialized Monte</line>
    <line x_offset="325.08" y_offset="18.25" spacing="0.9">4</line>
    <line x_offset="0.0" y_offset="13.56" spacing="-6.21">Carlo walks, each
consisting of 500 warm-up steps followed by 10 steps</line>
    <line x_offset="0.0" y_offset="0.0" spacing="2.65">with data
accumulation. Some representative error bars are also shown.</line>
    <component x="125.76" y="179.55" width="358.76" height="146.39"
page="15" page_width="612.0" page_height="792.0"/>
